<postlude component="profesor"> 

  <!-- Posibles errores -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students draw lines into the bars of the bar graph to find the number represented by the bar by counting.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>During the launch of the next day’s activity, have students discuss how the scale on the bar graph can be used to determine the number of people or objects in each category.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>